\id 1PE - Dawuro Full Bible Latin Version
\h 1 P'es'iroosa Kiitaa
\toc1 P'es'iroosi S'aafeedda Koyro Kiitaa
\toc2 1 P'es'iroosa Kiitaa
\toc3 1 P'es'.
\mt1 P'es'iroosi
\mt2 S'aafeedda Koyro Kiitaa
\imt1 Geluwaa
\ip Yesuusi kiitteedda P'es'iroosi s'aafeedda koyro kiitay s'aafetteeddawe, he kiitaa giddon «Dooretteedda S'oossaa asatuwaa» geetettiide s'eesettiyaanne K'eeri Iisiyaan huup'issa bagga shaakuwaan laaletteedda ammaniyaawanttussa. Ha kiitaa waanna k'ofay, ammanuwaa gaasuwaan metuunne waayyii gakkeeddawantta minisanaassanne mentsetsanaassa. S'aafii hawaa ootsiyaawe Aa hayk'uwaa, Aa dendduwaa, Aa laa'entso yuussaa odiyaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa nabbabiyaawantta hassayissiyaawaana. Unttunttu Yesuusi Kiristtoosa de'uwaa leemisuwaadan akkiide, metuwaa genc'c'iide aad'd'anaadan hassayissee. Hawaanna ittippe gatsiyaa wode, metuu unttunttu ammanuwaa s'alttatetsaa paac'c'iyaawaanne Yesuusi Kiristtoosi k'onc'c'iyaa gallassi unttunttu bessiyaa gatiyaa akkanaw de'iyaawaa unttuntta hassayissee.
\ip S'aafii, unttunttu metuwaan genc'c'ana mala mentsetsiyaawaa bollaakka, Kiristtoosa kaalliyaawanttu de'iyaawaadan unttunttu de'anaadan k'ofissee.
\iot Shemppatuwaa Ubbatoo Imetteedda K'antsa K'ofatuwaa
\io1 Geluwaa \ior 1:1-2\ior*
\io1 S'oossaa ashshuwaabaa \ior 1:3-12\ior*
\io1 Geeyyeedda de'uwaa de'anaadan imetteedda mak'k'uwaa \ior 1:13—2:10\ior*
\io1 Metuwaa wode ammaniyaa Asay ootsana bessiyaa aawotetsaa \ior 2:11—4:19\ior*
\io1 Ammaniyaa asaa ashikketetsaanne oosuwaa \ior 5:1-11\ior*
\io1 Wurssetsaa k'utiyaa \ior 5:12-14\ior*
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Taani, Yesuusi Kiristtoosi kiitteedda P'es'iroosi, S'oossay dooreedda asatoo P'ans's'oosa gadiyaan, Galaatiyaa gadiyaan, K'ap'p'adook'iyaa gadiyaan, Iisiyaa biittaaninne Biitaaniyaa gadiyaan betiyaan de'iyaawanttoo dabddaabbiyaa s'aafay.
\v 2 Yesuusi Kiristtoosaw hintte azazettana malanne Aa suutsan geeyyana mala, S'oossay Aawuu dooreedda hinttenttoo bare Ayyaanan geeshsheeddawanttoo, aad'd'o keekatetsaynne sarotetsay gido.
\s1 De'uwaa Immana Geedda Hidootaa
\p 
\v 3 Nuuni S'oossaa, nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa Aawuwaa, bare maarotetsaa daruwaadankka nuuna laa'entsuwaa yeleeddawaa, Yesuusi Kiristtoosa hayk'uwaappe dentseeddawaan nuw de'uwaa hidootaa immeeddawaa galateetto.
\v 4 K'ay S'oossay hinttenttoo immana daro laatay wook'k'ennawe, bayennawenne d'ayennawe saluwaan naagee.
\v 5 Hewekka hinttenttoo, S'oossaa wolk'k'aan ammanuwaan naagetti uttiide, atotetsaw giigeeddawanttoo wurssetsaa wodiyaan k'onc'c'anawaa.
\p 
\v 6 Ha"i guutsaa wodew haray atto dumma dumma paac'iyaan hintte paac'ettanaw koshshooppekka, hawaan daro nashettite.
\v 7 Hewe haray atto, tamaan yeggina d'ayiyaa work'k'aappekka hintte ammanuu daro al"onne bali bayinnawaa gidiyaawaa bessanaassa; yaatiide Yesuusi Kiristtoosi beettiyaa wode, galataa, bonchchuwaanne sabaa hintte akkana.
\v 8-9 Hintte Aa erana d'ayooppekka, siik'iita; hintte ha"i Aa be'ana d'ayooppekka, ammaniita. K'ay hintte hintte ammanoo polo gidiyaa hintte shemppuwaa atotetsaa akkiyaa diraw, odanaw danddayettenna bonchchuu kumeedda nashechchaa nashettiita.
\p 
\v 10 S'oossay hinttenttoo immana aad'd'o keekatetsaabaw timbbitiyaa odeedda nabatuu loytsi biddiide, ha atotetsaabaa koyyeeddino.
\v 11 Unttunttun de'iyaa Kiristtoosa Ayyaanay Kiristtoosa tuggaabaanne hewaappe guyyiyaan yaana bonchchuwaabaa kasetiide markkattiidde, awude woy waaneedda wodiyaan yaanenttonne akeekisseeddawaadan, unttunttu koyyeeddino.
\v 12 He timbbitiyaa odiyaawanttu ootseedda oosuu hinttessappe attin, unttunttu huup'iyaassa gidennawaa S'oossay unttunttoo k'onc'c'isseedda; ha"i hintte siseedda mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa hinttenttoo odeedda asatuu, barew saluwaappe kiitetteedda Geeshsha Ayaanaa wolk'k'an odeeddino. Hewaa kiitanchchatuukka be'anaw amottiino.
\s1 Geeshshatetsaan De'iyaawaa
\p 
\v 13 Hewaa diraw, oosuwaa ootsanaw hintte wozanaan k'ofaa giigissiidde hintte huup'iyaa naagite. Yesuusi Kiristtoosi k'onc'c'iyaa wode aad'd'o keekatetsaa hintte akkiyaa diraw, kumentsaa hidootaan naagite.
\v 14 S'oossaw azazettiyaa naanaadan; hintte kase erennaan amotteedda amuwaa kaalloppite.
\v 15-16 Shin hinttena s'eeseedda S'oossay geeshsha gideeddawaadan, hinttekka hintte oosuwaa ubbaan geeshsha gidite. S'oossaa Mas'aafan, «Taani geeshsha gidiyaa diraw, hinttekka geeshsha gidite» geetettiide s'aafetteedda.\x - \xo 1:15-16 \xt Wog. 11:44-45; 19:2\x*
\p 
\v 17 Asaa huup'iyaan huup'iyaan deemuwaa s'eellennan Aa oosuwaadan pirddiyaa S'oossaa woossiidde hintte, «Nu Aabboo» giide Aa s'eesiyaawaa gidooppe, ha alamiyaan bete gidiide hintte de'iyaa wodiyaan yashshatetsaan de'ite.
\v 18-19 Hintte hintte aawotuwaappe laatteedda patsenna de'uwaappe wozetteeddawe, d'ayiyaa biraa woy work'k'aa malaana gidennawaa eriita; borisiyaabay woy k'itay bayinna dorssaa suutsaadan, al"o Kiristtoosa suutsan hintte wozetteeddita.
\v 20 S'oossay sa'ay med'ettanaappe kase Kiristtoosa doori wotseedda; shin hintte diraw, ha wodiyaa wurssetsaan I beetteedda.
\v 21 Hintte ammanuunne hintte akkana giide nashechchan naagi utteeddabay S'oossaan de'ana mala, S'oossay hayk'uwaappe Aa dentsiide, aw bonchchuwaa immeeddawaa aan ammaniita.
\p 
\v 22 Tumatetsaw hintte azazettiyaawan, lo"a malatiyaa iitatetsay bayinnaan hintte ishatuwaa siik'anaw hintte huup'iyaa geeshshiide, ittuu ittuwaanna minisiide wozanaappe siik'ettite.
\p 
\v 23 Hintte hayk'k'iyaa zeretsaappe laa'entsuwaa yelettibeykkita; shin med'inaw de'iyaawaanne sintsawukka de'ana S'oossaa k'aalaan hayk'k'enna zeretsaappe yeletteeddita.
\v 24 Ayaw gooppe, S'oossaa Mas'aafay, «Asay ubbay maataa mala; Aa bonchchuu ubbaykka maataa c'iishshaa mala. Maatay melee; c'iishshaykka k'ok'k'ofettee.\x - \xo 1:24 \xt Isa. 40:6-8\x*
\v 25 Shin Godaa k'aalay med'inaw de'ee» yaagee. Hawe hinttenttoo Goday odeedda mishiraachchuwaa k'aalaa.
\c 2
\s1 De'uwaa Shuchchaanne Geeshsha Asaa
\p 
\v 1 Hewaa diraw, hintteppe iitatetsaa ubbaa, c'immiyaawaa ubbaa, lo"a malatiyaa iitatetsaa, k'anaatiyaanne zigirssaa ubbaa diggite.
\v 2-3 Goday keeka gideeddawaa hintte de'uwaan be'eeddawaa gidooppe, ha"i yeletteedda gac'ino naanatuwaadan, ushiidde dic'c'anawunne attanaw s'illo gideedda ayaanaa maatsaa laamotite.\x - \xo 2:2-3 \xt Maz. 34:8\x*
\p 
\v 4 Godaakko de'o shuchchaakko shiik'ite. Asay Aa is's'eedda; shin S'oossaa matan I dooretteedda al"o.
\v 5 Hinttekka k'ay de'o shuchchaadan, geeshsha k'eesaa gidiide, Yesuusi Kiristtoosa baggana S'oossaa nashechchiyaa ayaanaa yarshshuwaa S'oossaw yarshshanaw, hintte hintte huup'ew ayaana keetsaadan kees'ettite.
\v 6 Ayaw gooppe, S'oossaa Mas'aafay, «Be'ite, taani S'iyoone giyaa katamaan golliyaa godaa s'ap'uwaa minisiyaa, dooretteedda, al"o shuchchaa wotsay; aan ammaniyaa ooninne yeellatenna» yaagee.\x - \xo 2:6 \xt Isa. 28:16\x*
\v 7 Hewaa diraw, ha shuchchay hinttenttoo ammaniyaawanttoo daro al"a; shin ammanennawanttoo, «Gimbbiyaawanttu kad'eedda shuchchay godaa s'ap'uwaa minisiyaa, ubbaappe aad'd'iyaa shuchchaa gideedda» yaagee.
\v 8 K'aykka, «Ha shuchchay asaa d'ubbiyaa shuchchaanne asaa kunddissiyaa zaallaa» yaagee; unttunttu S'oossaa k'aalaa ammanenna diraw, unttunttoo kasenna k'ofetteeddawaadan d'ubetteeddino.\x - \xo 2:8 \xt Isa. 8:14-15\x*
\p 
\v 9 Shin S'oossay d'umaappe maalalissiyaa bare poo'oo hinttena s'eeseedda; hintte Aa ooratsa oosuwaa odanaw dooretteedda zare; hintte kaatiyaa k'eesatuwaa; geeshsha asanne S'oossaw buzo asaa.\x - \xo 2:9 \xt Kes. 19:5-6; Isa. 43:20, 21; Zar. 4:20; 7:6; 14:2; Tit. 2:14; Isa. 9:2\x*
\v 10 Hintte kase S'oossaa asaa gidikkita; shin ha"i hintte Aa asaa; hintte kase maarotetsaa akkibeykkita; shin ha"i maarotetsaa akkeeddita.\x - \xo 2:10 \xt Hos. 2:23\x*
\s1 S'oossaa Ayilatuwaa
\p 
\v 11 Ta dabbatoo, hintte ha sa'aan imatsaanne bete gidiide de'iyaawantta gideeddawaadan, ubbaa wode hintte shemppuwaanna olettiyaa asatetsaa amuwaappe hintte haakkana mala, taani hinttena woossay.
\v 12 Amanenna Asay hinttena iitabaa ootsiyaawanttudan zigiriyaa wode, Kiristtoosi yiyaa gallassi hintte lo"o oosuwaa unttunttu akeekiide, S'oossaa galatana mala, hintte de'uwaa unttunttu giddon loytsi naagite.
\p 
\v 13 Godaa diraw, asaa higgiyaa ubbaw moodettite; kaatiikka ubbaappe bolla gidiyaa diraw, aw moodettite.
\v 14 K'ay gadiyaa mooddiyaawanttookka moodettite. Ayaw gooppe, unttunttu iitabaa ootsiyaawantta muranawunne lo"obaa ootsiyaawantta galatanaw kaatiyaappe kiitetteeddino.
\v 15 Ayaw gooppe, S'oossay hintte hintte lo"o oosuwaan kad'iyaa eeyaa asatuwaa haasayaa c'o"u udanawaa koyyee.
\v 16 Ayiletetsaappe kesiide, S'oossaa ayiliyaadan de'iteppe attin, he ayiletetsaappe keseeddawaa iitatetsaa gentsiyaawaa ootsoppite.
\v 17 Asaa ubbaa bonchchite. Hintte ishatuwaa siik'ite. S'oossaw yayyite. Kaatiyaa bonchchite.
\s1 Kiristtoosa Gakkeedda Metuwaa Leemisuwaa
\p 
\v 18 Ayilatoo, hintte lo"o godatuwaa s'alalawunne ashikke godatuwaa s'alalaw gidennaan, iitatookka daro yayyiide moodettite.
\v 19 Ayaw gooppe, Asay naak'k'iyaa wode waayettiyaa uray S'oossaa k'oppiide, oge baynnaan naak'ettooppe S'oossay Aa anjjana.
\v 20 Ayaw gooppe, hintte nagaraa ootsina, hinttena dechchiyaa wode, hintte danddayooppe, hinttenttoo ay galatay de'ii? Shin lo"obaa ootsiide waayiyaa hintte danddayooppe, S'oossay hinttena hewoo anjjana.
\v 21 S'oossay hinttena s'eeseeddawe hewaa diraassa; ayaw gooppe, Kiristtoosi hinttenttoo waayettee; hintte Aa k'atamaa kaallana mala, hinttenttoo leemisuwaa gideedda.
\v 22 Nagaraa I ootsibeenna; bare doonaappe wordduwaa haasayibeenna.\x - \xo 2:22 \xt Isa. 53:9\x*
\v 23 Asay barena boriyaa wode, zaariide boribeenna; waayettiyaa wodekka manddibeenna. Shin s'illuwaa pirddiyaa S'oossaw barena aatsiide immeedda.\x - \xo 2:23 \xt Isa. 53:7\x*
\v 24 Nuuni nagaraw hayk'k'iide, s'illotetsaw de'ana mala, Kiristtoosi bare huup'ew bare ashuwaan nu nagaraa mask'k'aliyan tookkeedda; hintte Aa maytsaan pas'eeddita.\x - \xo 2:24 \xt Isa. 53:5\x*
\v 25 Ayaw gooppe, hintte ogii baleedda dorssaa mala; shin ha"i hintte shemppuwaa heemmiyaawaakkonne naagiyaawaakko simmeeddita.\x - \xo 2:25 \xt Isa. 53:6\x*
\c 3
\s1 Asinaabaanne Machchiyaabaa
\p 
\v 1-2 Hewaadankka machchetoo, hintte asinatuwaappe S'oossaa k'aalaw azazettena ittuu ittuu de'ooppekka, hintte palumettennan, unttunttu hintte yashshatetsaanne hintte geeshsha de'uwaa be'iide s'oonettana mala, unttunttoo moodettite.
\v 3 Hintte hintte huup'iyaa al"obaan giigissiyaawaaninne work'k'aa wotsiyaawaan woy al"o mayuwaa mayiyaawaan hinttenttu bolla bagga loytsoppite.
\v 4 Shin hintte garssan k'osetteedda asatetsaa lo"otetsay S'oossaa sintsan hinttenttoo daro al"o gidiide, d'ayenna ashikkenne woppu geedda ayaanaa gido.
\v 5 Ayaw gooppe, hewaadan S'oossaan hidooteedda geeshsha mac'c'a asatuu beni wode barenttu asinaw moodettiide, barentta daro loytseeddino.
\v 6 Hewaadan Saara Abraahaama, «Ta godaw» yaaga s'eesaadde, aw azazettaaddu; hinttekka ittibawunne yayyenaan lo"obaa ootsooppe, I naanatuwaa.\x - \xo 3:6 \xt Dom. 18:12\x*
\p 
\v 7 Hewaadan asinatoo, hintte mac'c'a asatuwaana akeekan ittippe de'ite. Unttunttoo daaburanchcha asatetsay de'iyaa diraw, unttuntta bonchchite; hintte woosay d'ubettenna mala, S'oossay immeedda de'uwaa aad'd'o keekatetsaa unttunttu hinttenanna ittippe laattino.
\s1 Lo"obaa Ootsiidde Metuwaa Akkiyaawaa
\p 
\v 8 Wurssetsaan, ubbay itti k'ofaan de'ite. Ittuu ittoo k'arettite; ishatuwaadan siik'ettite; k'ay ittuu ittoo keekiyaawanttanne hintte huup'iyaa kawushshiyaawantta gidite.
\v 9 Iitaa diraw iitaa woy shek'aa diraw shek'aa zaaroppite; hewaa aggiide, S'oossay hinttenttu anjjuwaa laattanaadan hinttena s'eeseedda diraw, anjjite.
\v 10 Ayaw gooppe, S'oossaa Mas'aafay hawaadan yaagee; «De'uwaa dosiyaawenne lo"o gallassaa be'anaw koyyiyaawe oona gidooppenne bare ins's'arssan iitabaa haasayiyaawaanne wordduwaa odiyaawaa aggo.\x - \xo 3:10 \xt Maz. 34:12-16\x*
\p 
\v 11 «Iitabaa ootsiyaawaa aggiide, lo"obaa ootso; sarotetsaakka loytsi koyyonne kaallanaw baas'eto.
\p 
\v 12 «Ayaw gooppe, Godaa ayfii s'illotuwaakko s'eellee; k'ay Aa haytsay ubbaa wode unttunttu woosaw dooyaa de'ee. Shin Goday iitabaa ootsiyaawantta bare hank'k'uwaa som"iyaan s'eellee» yaagee.
\p 
\v 13 Hintte lo"obaa ootsanaw amottooppe, hinttena k'ohanawe oonee?
\v 14 Shin haray atto, s'illotetsaa diraw hintte waayettooppekka, anjjetteeddawantta. Asaw yayyoppitenne hirggoppite.\x - \xo 3:14 \xt Mat. 5:10; Isa. 8:12-13\x*
\v 15 Shin Kiristtoosa hintte wozanaan bonchchitenne Aa hintte Godaa ootsite. S'oossay hinttenttoo hidooteedda de'oo gaasuwaa oochchiyaa oossinne zaaruwaa immanaw ubbaa wode giigi uttite;
\v 16 shin hewaa ashikketetsaaninne yashshatetsaan ootsite. K'ay Kiristtoosan hintte de'iyaa lo"o de'uwaa iitabaa ootseeddawaadan, hintte bollan iitabaa haasayiyaa Asay bare zigiriyaawaan yeellatana mala, hintte wozanay geeshsha gido.
\v 17 Ayaw gooppe, S'oossay geeddawaa gidooppe, iitabaa ootseedda diraw waayettiyaawaappe, lo"obaa ootseedda diraw waayettiyaawe keeka.
\v 18 Ayaw gooppe, Kiristtoosi nuuna S'oossaakko afanaw, barew s'illo gidiidde, makkalanchchatuwaa diraw, itti gede ubbaa nagaraw hayk'k'eedda; I bare asatetsan hayk'k'eedda; shin ayyaanan pas'eedda.
\v 19 K'ay he Ayyaanan, k'ashuwaan de'iyaa ayyaanatuwaakko biide, unttunttoo k'aalaa odeedda.
\v 20 He ayyaanatuu amareeda, hosppun asatuu haatsaan atteedda markkabiyaa Nohe kees's'ishshin, S'oossay danddayiide gam"eedda wode, S'oossaw azazettibeena asaa ayyaanatuwaa.\x - \xo 3:20 \xt Dom. 6:1—7:24\x*
\v 21 Hewe s'ink'k'ataw leemisuwaa gidiide, hinttena ha"i ashshee; suure wozanaappe S'oossaa woossiyaawaappe attin, bollaa k'itaa meec'c'iyaawaa gidenna; hewe hinttena Yesuusi Kiristtoosi hayk'uwaappe denddeeddawaan ashshee.
\v 22 Saluwaa biide S'oossaappe ushechcha baggan I uttiide, kiitanchchaa ubbaa, maataanna de'iyaawanttanne wolk'k'aamatuwaa mooddee.
\c 4
\s1 Geeshshatetsaan De'ana De'uwaabaa
\p 
\v 1 Hewaa diraw, Kiristtoosi bare ashuwaan nuw waayetteedda diraw, hinttekka he k'ofaan danc'c'ettite. Ayaw gooppe, bare ashuwaan waayetteedda uray nagaraa ootsiyaawaa aggeedda.
\v 2 Hawaappe sintsan, ha sa'aan shemppuwaanna de'anaw atteedda wodiyaan, S'oossay koyyiyaawaadan de'anaw bessiyaawaappe attin, asaa amuwaadan de'anaw bessena.
\v 3 Ayaw gooppe, ammanenna Asay ootsanaw dosiyaawaa hintte ootsiidde, woshummanaw kajjeeliyaawaan, amuwaan, matsuwaan, yetsaan, ushshaan, pokkiyaa eek'aw goyinniyaawan, de'eedda kase aad'd'eedda wodii hinttenttoo gidanawaa.
\v 4 Ammanenna asaana hintte shoray bayinna oosuwaa ittippe ootsenna diraw maalalettiide, hinttena boriino.
\v 5 Shin unttunttu pas'a de'iyaa asaa bollanne hayk'k'eedda asaa bolla pirddanaw giigi utteedda S'oossaw zaaruwaa immana.
\v 6 Hayk'k'eedda asay\f + \fr 4:6 \fq Hayk'k'eedda asay: \ft Yesuusa ammananaappe kasenna hayk'k'eeddawantta woy Nohe wode asatuwaa. \xt 3:19\xt*\ft s'eellite.\f* bare asatetsan Asay pirddettiyaawaadan pirddettanawunne k'ay ayyaanan S'oossay de'iyaawaadan de'anaw, wonggalaa mishiraachchuu unttunttoo hewoo odetteedda.
\s1 S'oossay Immeedda Imotatuwaa Loytsi Ayissiyaawaa
\p 
\v 7 Ubbabawukka wurssetsay matatteedda. Hewaa diraw, S'oossaa woossanaw k'ofaan geeyyiide, hinttena naagitenne minnite.
\v 8 Siik'uu daro nagaraa kammiyaa diraw, ubbabaappe aatsiide ittuu ittuwaanna wozanaappe siik'ettite.\x - \xo 4:8 \xt Lem. 10:12\x*
\v 9 Zuuzummennan ittuu ittuwaa imatsatetsaan mokkite.
\v 10 Hintte huup'iyaan huup'iyaan S'oossaappe dumma dumma aad'd'o keekatetsaa akkeeddawaadankka, S'oossaa dumma imuwaa hadaraa loytsi kesiyaawanttudan, ittuu ittoo ootsite.
\v 11 Yesuusi Kiristtoosa baggana ubbabaan S'oossay galatettana mala, ooninne odiyaawaa gidooppe, k'aalaa S'oossaappe akkiide odiyaawaadan odo. K'ay ooninne maaddiyaawaa gidooppe, S'oossay aw immiyaa wolk'k'an maaddo. Bonchchuunne godatetsay S'oossaw med'inaappe med'inaw gido. Amen"i.
\s1 Metuwaa Wode Minniyaawaa
\p 
\v 12 Ta siik'atoo, hintte giddon tamaadan guuddiidde paac'c'iyaa waayyii yiyaawaa ooratsabay haniyaawaadan malalettoppite.
\v 13 Shin Kiristtoosa bonchchuu beettiyaa wode hintte nashettana mala, aanana waayettiyaawaan nashetite.
\v 14 Asay hinttena Kiristtoosa suntsaa diraw boriyaawaa gidooppe, hintte anjjetteeddawantta; ayaw gooppe, bonchcho Ayyaanay, S'oossaa Ayyaanay, hintte bolla shemppana.
\v 15 Hintteppe ooninne shemppuwaa wod'eeddawaadan, woy kayisuwaadan, woy iitabaa ootseedda asaadan, woy hara asaa yewuwaa geleeddawaadan waayettoppo.
\v 16 Shin ooninne Kiristtaaniyaa gidiyaa diraw waayettooppe, Kiristtoosa suntsaa diraw, S'oossaa galatanaappe attin, yeellatoppo.
\p 
\v 17 Ayaw gooppe, pirdday S'oossaa golliyaan doomettiyaa wodii gakkeedda. K'ay he pirdday koyiro nu bolla doomettiyaawaa gidooppe, Aa wonggalaw azazettenawanttu wurssetsay ayaa gidanee?
\v 18 S'illo Asay tuggaan attiyaawaa gidooppe, makkalanchchaynne nagaranchchay yaatina waananee?\x - \xo 4:18 \xt Lem. 11:31\x*
\v 19 Hewaa diraw k'ay, S'oossay geeddawaadan waayettiyaawanttu lo"obaa ootsiidde, barenttu shemppuwaa hadaraa barena med'd'eedda ammanettiyaa S'oossaw immino.
\c 5
\s1 S'oossaa Asaa Ayissanaw Imetteedda Zoriyaa
\p 
\v 1 Simmi taani woosa golliyaa c'imatuwaanna c'ima gidiyaawenne, Kiristtoosa waayiyaa markkattiyaawe, k'ay k'onc'c'ana bonchchuwaa shaakkanawe hintte giddon de'iyaa c'imatuwaa zoray.
\v 2 Hintte giddon de'iyaa S'oossaa wudiyaa S'oossay koyyiyaawaadan heemmite. Dosuwaanappe attin, wolk'k'an gidenna. K'ay hintte go"a s'alalaa s'eellennan, lo"o k'ofaan heemmite.
\v 3 Wudew hintte leemisuwaa giditeppe attin, hintte heemmiyaawantta wolk'k'aan heemmoppite.
\v 4 K'ay heemmiyaawanttu kaappuu k'onc'c'iyaa wode, bayenna bonchcho kalachchaa hintte akkana.
\p 
\v 5 Hewaadankka yalaga asatoo, c'imatoo moodettite. Ubbaykka ittuu ittoo ootsanaw hintte huup'iyaa kawushshiyaawaa afilaadan mayyite. Ayaw gooppe, S'oossay otorettiyaawantta is's'ee; shin barena kawushshiyaawanttoo aad'd'o keekatetsaa immee.\x - \xo 5:5 \xt Lem. 3:34\x*
\v 6 S'oossay bare lo"o wodiyaan hinttena d'ok'k'u ootsana mala, wolk'k'aama S'oossaa kushiyaappe garssanna hinttena toochchite.
\v 7 I hinttenttoo k'oppiyaa diraw, hinttena hirggissiyaa ubbabaa Aa bolla olite.
\p 
\v 8 S'alahiyaa kaappuu, hintte morkkii, mittiyaa uraa koyyiide, gudiyaa gaammuwaadan hintte yuushshuwaan yuuyyiyaa diraw naagettitenne beegottite.
\v 9 Sa'aan de'iyaa hintte ishatuu hewaadan waayettiyaawaa eriide, ammanuwaan minniide, aanana ek'ettite.
\v 10 Aad'o keekatetsaa ubbaa S'oossay, bare med'inaa bonchchoo Kiristtoosi Yesuusa baggana hinttena s'eeseeddawe, amareeda wodiyaa hintte waayetteeddawaappe guyyiyaan, I bare huup'ew hinttena shiri ooratsananne minisana. K'ay I hinttena maaddananne baasi essana.
\v 11 Wolk'k'ay med'inaappe med'inaa gakkanaw aw gido. Amen"i.
\s1 Wurssetsa Sarotaa
\p 
\v 12 Hawe S'oossaa tumu aad'd'o keekatetsaa gidiyaawaa taani hinttenttoo markkattaaddenne hinttena zoraadde, hinttenttoo k'antsaan s'aafeedda dabddaabbiyaa ammanettiyaa ishaa gaade taani k'oppiyaa Sillaase bolla kiittaad; he aad'd'o keekatetsan minneeddita.
\p 
\v 13 Hinttenana ittippe dooretteedda Baabloonen\f + \fr 5:13 \fq Baabloone: \ft Sas'aa Mas'aafaa k'ofaadan, ha suntsay Roome guussaa gidennaan aggena.\f* de'iyaa woosa golliyaa asaynne ta na'ay Mark'k'oossi hinttena «Saro saro» giino.
\v 14 Siik'uwaa yeretaa yerettiidde, ittuu ittuwaa sarotite.
\p Hinttew, Kiristtoosanna ittuwaa gideeddawanttoo ubbatoo sarotetsay gido. Amen"i.
